    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given the medium model influence and documented engineering judgment. Supporting evidence from experimental validation studies and mesh convergence analyses informed this determination.",
